Package: ItemRest
Title: Automated Item Removal Strategies for Exploratory Factor Analysis
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person(given = "Ahmet", family = "Çalışkan",
             email = "ahmetcaliskan1987@gmail.com",
             role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Automates the identification and comparative evaluation of item-removal strategies in exploratory factor analysis, producing transparent summaries (explained variance, loading ranges, reliability) to support comfortable, replicable decisions.
